                                                <div class="fusion-text fusion-text-1"
                                                    style="--awb-text-transform:none;--awb-margin-top:20px;">
                                                    <p>Hi, I’m Julie, the owner of Moonrise Crystals. When I originally
                                                        started Moonrise Crystals I didn’t reveal very much about my own
                                                        background, but I’ve since learned people are sometimes just as
                                                        curious about me as I am about them. So for those curious ones –
